import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import "bootstrap"

import { createApp } from 'vue'

import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'

import App from './App.vue'

import InicioPage from '@/pages/InicioPage.vue'
//import HotelsPage from '@/pages/VerHtl.vue'
import HotelPage from '@/pages/HotelesCrear.vue'
import HabitacionesPage from '@/pages/HabitacionesTipo.vue'
import AcomodacionesPage from '@/pages/AcomodacionesHotel.vue'


const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: [
        //{patch: '/', name:'InicioPage', component: InicioPage},
        {patch: '/Crear', name:'HotelPage', component: HotelPage},
        {patch: '/Ver', name:'InicioPage', component: InicioPage},
        {patch: '/Tipo', name:'HabitacionesPage', component: HabitacionesPage},
        {patch: '/Acomod', name:'AcomodacionesPage', component: AcomodacionesPage}
    ]
})


createApp(App)
.use(router)
.mount('#app')
